In order to use you need to follow these instructions

1. create a folder called songs, here you are going to store your files
2. then create a folder with the name of the song.
3. When your in that folder. you need to upload two files. A wav file(with the song) and a png file(the cover).
4. name the wav file "song" and the png file "wav"
5. Thats everything you need to know, now you can import as many songs as you like!
